import React from 'react'
import { Routes ,Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Aside from './Aside'
import Nav from './Nav'
import BlogList from './pages/BlogList'


function AdminPanel() {
    return (

           <>
            <Nav />
            <Aside />

            <Routes>
            <Route path="admin/bloglist" element={<BlogList/>}/>
            </Routes>


            </>

    )
}

export default AdminPanel
